gc01.cw.robf.model

Class OrderModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gc01.cw.robf.model.OrderModel

  • public class OrderModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Model for Order objects. Uses Property and Observable types for most variables to allow JavaFX tableView refresh.

    Returning current date-time adapted from https://www.mkyong.com/java/java-how-to-get-current-date-time-date-and-calender/

    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Rob Farthing

        public OrderModel(java.lang.Integer tableNumber)

        Parameters:
        tableNumber - Integer value of table number to create order against.
